data.title: Asteroids Names
data.meta_description: Asteroids Names - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of over 79,000 names beginning with letters A through D that have been approved by the International Astronomical Union for naming minor planets and other celestial bodies. The names include individuals from various cultures and time periods as well as places, concepts and fictional characters.
